ed="T" n="0802b26"/><persName key="A011073">釋省躬</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000011923"><placeName>睦州</placeName><placeName>桐廬</placeName></placeName>人也。為童強識，耆宿呼語，<lb
ed="T" n="0802b27"/>怪其志大而言高。<anchor xml:id="beg0802002"/>每<anchor xml:id="end0802002"/>厭樊籠。忽投<placeName key="PL000000011900">聖德寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0802b28"/>慕道從師，勅恩得度。性靈天發，於毘<anchor xml:id="beg0802sgsz7"/>尼<anchor xml:id="end0802sgsz7"/>道，<lb
ed="T" n="0802b29"/>學如溫習。復擇名師，得<placeName key="PL000000009882"><placeName>姑蘇</placeName><placeName>開元</placeName></placeName><persName key="A011021">道恒<roleName>師</roleName></persName>。<pb ed="T" n="0802c" xml:id="T50.2061.0802c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0802c01"/><persName key="A011021">恒</persName>曰：「甚矣！<ref type="person" target="#A011021">吾</ref>得<persName key="A011073">躬</persName>也，門人日益親。<ptr target="#n2357"/>」及乎探<lb
ed="T" n="0802c02"/><anchor xml:id="beg0802sgsz9"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>頤</sic><corr>賾</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0802sgsz9"/>精微，愈征愈遠。時有擊論互指為迷者，<lb
ed="T" n="0802c03"/>必請見<persName key="A011073">躬</persName>為其判之，坐分曲直。諺曰：「義<lb
ed="T" n="0802c04"/>盡<persName key="A011073">省躬</persName>。」言到<persName key="A011073">躬</persName>義無不盡也。其博綜律乘，<lb
ed="T" n="0802c05"/>扞禦師門也若此。<persName key="A011021">恒</persName>曰：「自<ref type="person" target="#A011021">吾</ref>有<persName key="A011073">躬</persName>也，惡言<lb
ed="T" n="0802c06"/>不聞矣。<ptr target="#n1870"/>」<persName key="A011073">躬</persName>避席葉拱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g584"/>而對曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A011073">某</ref>不佞也，仰<lb
ed="T" n="0802c07"/><ref type="person" target="#A011021">師</ref>之道，若<anchor xml:id="beg0802003"/>採<anchor xml:id="end0802003"/>扶桑以啖𧔞蠶。所患者，未<lb
ed="T" n="0802c08"/>能嘔繁絲以報主耳。」<persName key="A011021">恒</persName>曰：「視<ref type="person" target="#A011073">子</ref>吐<persName key="A023331">園客</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0802c09"/>五色絲<ptr target="#n1744"/>，可供黼繡<ptr type="glossary" target="#g585"/>之資。言太謙矣。」晚赴<placeName key="PL000000010783">維<lb
ed="T" n="0802c10"/><anchor xml:id="beg0802sgsz11"/>揚<anchor xml:id="end0802sgsz11"/></placeName>之召，廣訓徒焉。然其滿口雌黃，品藻<ptr type="glossary" target="#g587"/>否<lb
ed="T" n="0802c11"/>臧古今之義。生徒明敏者各錄之。都加潤色，<lb
ed="T" n="0802c12"/>號《順正記》十卷<ptr target="#n1745"/>，行之。復著《分輕重物儀》別<lb
ed="T" n="0802c13"/>行，沿襲《十三章門條例》，外加近世現有物之<lb
ed="T" n="0802c14"/>重輕<ptr type="glossary" target="#g570"/>，頗為要用。<persName key="A011073">躬</persName>復高儒學，作碑頌越多<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2070"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0802c15"/>以其曾化<placeName key="PL000000010783"><anchor xml:id="beg0802004"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>邪</sic><corr>邗</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0802004"/>溝</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g588"/>，故呼<persName key="A011073">淮南記主</persName>，自號<persName key="A011073">清冷<lb
ed="T" n="0802c16"/>山沙門</persName>焉。</p>
